title: About
----
<p>I've been working with web design, hosting and programming in a professional capacity part-time since 2000, and became a full-time freelancer as of July 2015.</p>
<p>Outside of work, I run <a href="http://www.currybeer.com">Currybeer</a> and <a href="http://www.geekwalks.co.uk">Geek Walks</a>, edit the <a href="http://www.flossuk.org/">FLOSS UK</a> newsletter, and act as treasurer and webmaster for the <a href="http://www.manchesterca.org.uk">Manchester Classical Association</a>. I'm also a regular attendee at <a href="http://www.manlug.org" target="_blank">ManLUG</a> and have given <a href="http://www.phpdeveloper.org.uk/talks/">talks</a> on a variety of subjects.</p>
<p>I have also served on a number of boards, including <a href="https://www.directfleetinsurance.co.uk">Direct Fleet Insurance</a>, <a href="http://www.ukuug.org" target="_blank">UKUUG</a> (now <a href="http://www.flossuk.org">FLOSS UK</a>), <a href="http://www.merci.org.uk" target="_blank">MERCi</a> and <a href="http://www.boltoncab.co.uk/">Citizens Advice Bolton</a>.</p>
